## 🏗️ 생성자 패턴

### 패턴 1: `new()` - 표준 생성자

```rust
impl User {
    fn new(name: &str, age: u32) -> User {
        User {
            name: String::from(name),
            age,
        }
    }
}

let user = User::new("Alice", 25);
```

**용도**: 기본적인 초기화

### 패턴 2: `from_*()` - 변환 생성자

```rust
impl User {
    fn from_string(data: String) -> User {
        let parts: Vec<&str> = data.split(',').collect();
        User {
            name: String::from(parts[0]),
            age: parts[1].parse().unwrap_or(0),
        }
    }
}

let user = User::from_string("Alice,25".to_string());
```

**용도**: 다른 타입에서 변환

### 패턴 3: 빌더 패턴 (Builder Pattern)

```rust
impl ConfigBuilder {
    fn new() -> ConfigBuilder {
        ConfigBuilder {
            timeout: 5000,
            retries: 3,
            debug: false,
        }
    }

    fn with_timeout(mut self, timeout: u32) -> ConfigBuilder {
        self.timeout = timeout;
        self
    }

    fn build(self) -> Config {
        Config {
            timeout: self.timeout,
            retries: self.retries,
            debug: self.debug,
        }
    }
}

let config = ConfigBuilder::new()
    .with_timeout(10000)
    .build();
```

**용도**: 복잡한 객체 생성, 선택적 필드

